<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١ - يَا عَمْرُو وَالأَمْثَالُ يَضْـ ... ـرِبُهَا لِذِي الْعَقْل الْحَكِيمُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢ - دُمْ للْخَلِيلِ بِوُدِّه ... مَا خَيْرُ وُدٍّ لا يَدُومُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣١٨)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ يَحْيَى بْنُ زِيَادٍ الْحَارِثِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الخفيف)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - ولَقَدْ أَمْنَحُ الصَّدِيقَ وِدَادًا ... لا مَزِيجًا لَدَيَّ حُلْوًا مَذَاقُهْ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - ولَقَدْ أَمنَحُ الْمَوَدَّةَ إِخْوَا ... ني إِذَا الْوُدُّ خَانَه مذَّاقُهْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٣١٩)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضًا:</span> <span class="c2">(المتقارب)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ - وَأَعْقِدُ بالْوُدِّ حَبْلَ الصَّفَاء ... إِذَا غَيَّرَ الْوُدَّ خَوَّانُهُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢٠)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ صَالِحُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْقُدُّوسِ الأَزْدِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١ - وَصَافِ إِذَا صَافَيْتَ بِالْوُدِّ خَالِصًا ... تَجدْ مِثْلَ مَا أَخْلَصْتَ عِنْدَ ذَوِي الْوُدِّ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٣٢١)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَقَال أَيْضًا:</span> <span class="c2">(الخفيف)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١ - إِنْ رَضيتَ الصَّديِقَ فَاصْدُقْهُ في الْوُدِّ ... فَخَيْرُ الْوِدَادِ مَا صُدِقَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>